subject: Trades (Sports)
Baseball
lead_paragraph: R. A. Dickey’s value turned out to be worth two of the Blue Jays’ top prospects, Travis d’Arnaud, a 23-year-old catcher, and the 20-year-old right-hander Noah Syndergaard.
